            <div class="panel-heading our_panel_heading">
                <div class="panel-title our_panel_title">
                    <p class="our_panel_p">
                        What are badges?
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-resize-vertical"
                              style="float: right;">
                        </span>
                    </p>
                </div><!-- end 'panel-title'\'our_panel_title' divs -->
            </div><!-- end 'panel-heading'\'our_panel_heading' divs -->
        </a><!-- end '#accordian_03' id + '#collapse_CM' href -->

        <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapse_CM">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>
                    Badges are a fun way to visualize what kind of pets you own or what kind of animals you specialize in providing services for.
                    With badges, other people will be able to look at your profile at a glance and learn a little more about you.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Owner badges show what kind of animals you own, whereas provider badges will tell others which animals you specialize in working with.
                </p>
            </div><!-- end 'panel-body' div -->
        </div><!--end 'panel-collapse'\'collapse' div + '#collapse_CM' id -->
    </div><!-- end 'panel'\'our_panel_01' div -->

